<h2 style="padding: 15px 25px;">We'll update your social media, for free.</h2>

<div class="row info-section" style="background-color: #54799b;">
	<div class="col col-md-4 col-sm-12 col-sm-push-6">
		<%= image_tag('example posts.png') %>
	</div>
	<div class="col col-md-4 col-md-offset-1 col-sm-12 col-sm-pull-4" >
		<div>
			<h4 class="title" style="color: #f6f6f6;"><strong>Spend your time on something else</strong></h4>
			<p style="color: #f6f6f6;" >Delegate your social media to our automated post schedule. We'll handle the images, captions, hashtags, seasons, and timing so you don't have to.</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>

<div class="row info-section" style="background-color: #ceddea;">
	<div class="col col-md-4 col-md-offset-1 col-sm-12">
		<%= image_tag("https://storage.googleapis.com/promoposts/web_assets/overlay.gif") %>
	</div>
	<div class="col col-md-4 col-md-offset-1 col-sm-12" >
		<div>
			<h4 class="title" style="color: #2d4059;"><strong>It's for you</strong></h4>
			<p style="color: #2d4059;" >Automatically overlay your logo on top of the images. Choose topics most relevant to your business, and we'll post about it.</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>

<div class="row info-section" style="background-color: #d7ebf2;">
	<div class="col col-md-4 col-sm-12 col-sm-push-6">
		<%= image_tag('banner and cover photo.png') %>
	</div>
	<div class="col col-md-4 col-md-offset-1 col-sm-12 col-sm-pull-4" >
		<div>
			<h4 class="title" style="color: #2d4059;"><strong>Level up your digital presence with our content gallery</strong></h4>
			<p style="color: #2d4059;">Explore different types of assets including cover photos, email banners, and memes in our digital gallery. Download campaigns with multiple assets keep your online voice consistent.</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>

<div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 15px;">
	<%= button_to "Get Started", signup_path, method: :get, class: "btn-submit" %>
</div>

